com.interpss.core.algo.mslf

Interface MultiStateAclfAlgorithm<TNet extends AclfNetwork>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BaseMultiStateLfAlgorithm<TNet>, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, NetworkRef<TNet>, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MultiStateAclfAlgorithmImpl

    public interface MultiStateAclfAlgorithm<TNet extends AclfNetwork>
extends BaseMultiStateLfAlgorithm<TNet>
    A representation of the model object 'Multi State Aclf Algorithm'. Class for defining a multiple state algorithm object. It contains a basecase AclfNetwork object, a set of cloned AclfNetwork objects, and a set of SenAnalysisAlgorithm objects. The cloned AclfNetwork object and the SenAnalysisAlgorithm object has 1 - many relationship.

    The following features are supported:

    • Ms Aclf Algo List
    See Also:
    MslfAlgorithmPackage.getMultiStateAclfAlgorithm()
